                           Signs Of Life - Pink Floyd

                         Transcribed by Mike Bremford
                       From "A Momentary Lapse of Reason"

Notation:
 <12>           Natural Harmonic            ===>          Hold a bend
 7/10           Slide                       5/(.5)        Bend a quarter step.
 7/(10)         Bend                        (10)\7        Release a bend


